snippet.title: Welcome to the NEW Webkinz!
snippet.description:
Look for Webkinz Next on your favorite app store! https://bit.ly/3eLgB8o - Microsoft Store (Windows) https://apple.co/3eKdb5K - App Store (iOS) https://bit.ly/3ya1Tzw - Play Store (Android)

Learn to play the new Webkinz game! Earn KinzCash to take care of your pets and decorate their home.
